'''Shahaadah''' ([[luuqada carabiga]]: {{lang|ar|الشهادة}}), ama shahaado waxa weeye qirista Ilaahay in uu yahay hal kaliya waaxid maba tawxis ka oo ah qirista ilaahy.
shahadah waxey ka mid tahay shanta tiir oo ugu muhiimsan diinta [[Islaam]]ka, waxaana weeye tiirk koowad oo ah shahaadada.

== Akhrinta ==

أشهد أن لا إله إلاَّ الله و أشهد أن  محمد رسول الله (luuqada carabiga)

Waxaan qirayaa in uusan jirin ilaah, Alle (''Allaah'') mooye, waxana qirayaa in uu nabi Muxamed yahay rasuulkii Alle (''Allaah'').

I testify that there is no god (ilah) but God (Allah), and I testify that] Muhammad is the messenger of God (English) 
